{"id":191,"date":"2024-06-28T13:02:18","date_gmt":"2024-06-28T13:02:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/lighthq.com.ng\/ace\/?page_id=191"},"modified":"2024-09-12T17:13:17","modified_gmt":"2024-09-12T17:13:17","slug":"women-youth-empowerment","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/our-work\/women-youth-empowerment\/","title":{"rendered":"Economic Empowerment"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"191\" class=\"elementor elementor-191\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-66d011a6 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"66d011a6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;gradient&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1f405806 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1f405806\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-525f12e7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"525f12e7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Economic Empowerment<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-670c0098 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"670c0098\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9bd8a01 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"9bd8a01\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1ff95b40 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1ff95b40\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"740\" height=\"596\" src=\"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Artboard-1-kk.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-30145\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Artboard-1-kk.png 740w, https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Artboard-1-kk-300x242.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3cf3547f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3cf3547f\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-163c4a53 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"163c4a53\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Business Empowerment Programme for Women (BEPW)<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5a9d593c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5a9d593c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In June 2017, ACE Charity launched the Business Empowerment\u00a0 Program for Women (BEPW) in partnership with Transcorp Hilton,\u00a0 Abuja. The program, which runs twice a year for six months, is aimed\u00a0 at empowering young women from disadvantaged communities with basic sewing and business\u00a0 management skills which will enable them to gain the necessary\u00a0 knowledge to establish and manage their own businesses effectively\u00a0 and efficiently.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">During the course of the training, the beneficiaries receive free\u00a0 transportation to and from the training venue as well as free feeding.\u00a0 At the end of the training, the beneficiaries gain skills needed to start and run a successful fashion and designing business, and the\u00a0 brand new sewing machines they learn with are gifted to them to help kick start their businesses. Since its inception, a total of 48\u00a0 young women have been empowered.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5027381b elementor-mobile-align-center elementor-hidden-desktop elementor-hidden-tablet elementor-hidden-mobile elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"5027381b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Join the BEPW Waitlist<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-73a8b26 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"73a8b26\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-acc210c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"acc210c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6559a2c6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6559a2c6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Women MicroCredit Programme (WMP)<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1a78a4ea elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1a78a4ea\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rural women entrepreneurs are significant development partners, as their engagement in economic activities creates monetary gains, decreases the poverty rate, increases self-employment and employment of others. It is therefore crucial that they are prioritised in economic recovery efforts.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We empower rural women entrepreneurs with small-scale, interest-free loans to support their businesses. We provide them with access to formal banking services by opening bank accounts for them and training them on how to use mobile banking,\u00a0 ensuring\u00a0 financial inclusion and an easier method to transact.\u00a0 In addition, we train our entrepreneurs on business management, financial literacy in order to prepare them for success.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Over 300 women are currently enrolled in the programme. The Women Microcredit Programme has economically empowered rural women enterprises through increased revenues and savings among beneficiaries, increased access to digital banking services, business expansion, and starting of new businesses. <\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6d102e26 elementor-mobile-align-center elementor-hidden-desktop elementor-hidden-tablet elementor-hidden-mobile elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"6d102e26\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Apply for a MicroCredit<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-21ac0169 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"21ac0169\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1c2c78bb elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1c2c78bb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1425\" height=\"950\" src=\"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/SSK_6177.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-30321\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/SSK_6177.jpg 1425w, https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/SSK_6177-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/SSK_6177-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/SSK_6177-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1425px) 100vw, 1425px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a92538a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a92538a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-91d56a5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"91d56a5\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2ae6dcb elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"2ae6dcb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1350\" height=\"900\" src=\"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/SSK_0129.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-30325\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/SSK_0129.jpg 1350w, https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/SSK_0129-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/SSK_0129-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/SSK_0129-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1350px) 100vw, 1350px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-baab14d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"baab14d\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b9348c7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b9348c7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Careers@Hilton<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-84fb950 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"84fb950\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nigeria is currently facing an unemployment crisis. According to the National Bureau of <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Statistics, about 42% of Nigerians are unemployed, one of the highest in the world, and many <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nigerian youth have been termed \u201cunemployable\u201d because they lack the essential skills <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">employers need.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Since 2013, ACE Charity, in partnership with Transcorp Hilton, has improved the employability <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">of about 250 unemployed young Nigerians by providing them with the relevant work <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">experience and soft skills needed to kickstart their careers. This is achieved by placing the <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">beneficiaries in various departments of Transcorp Hilton, based on their career goals, where <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">they gain hands-on experience to improve their technical skills. The programme also offers <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">daily mentorship sessions led by industry experts, where they acquire transferable soft skills <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">like confidence, leadership, public speaking, decision-making, goal-setting and professional <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">communication. These skills enable them to effectively compete for job opportunities and set <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">a strong foundation for their careers. After the program\u2019s completion, participants not only <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">gain the essential technical and soft skills but receive continuous mentorship and long-term <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">support to ensure continued growth.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Since the program&#8217;s inception, the program has seen positive results. Over 90% of the <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">participants have reported improved soft skills. Additionally, Transcorp Hilton has employed <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">about 10% of the participants, while others have obtained jobs and started their businesses. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These successes highlight the program\u2019s effectiveness in addressing unemployment and <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">improving the employability of young Nigerians.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2848282 elementor-mobile-align-center elementor-hidden-desktop elementor-hidden-tablet elementor-hidden-mobile elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"2848282\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Join the BEPW Waitlist<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7e68277 elementor-hidden-desktop elementor-hidden-tablet elementor-hidden-mobile e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7e68277\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6b6ac71 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"6b6ac71\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9dd3651 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9dd3651\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Careers @ Hilton<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b02bd48 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b02bd48\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The Careers at Hilton programme is an initiative of ACE Charity in partnership with Transcorp Hilton Abuja. The objective of the programme is to provide an opportunity for youths to gain relevant work experience at the Hilton, where they learn transferable skills that will enable them to compete better for economic opportunities in society. Participants are engaged in daily mentorship sessions and are provided with lunch and transportation by Transcorp Hilton for the duration of their internship.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-232bed8 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"232bed8\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cf49998 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"cf49998\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"270\" height=\"213\" src=\"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/training-session-1-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-83\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c8b79a5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c8b79a5\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-00bbf40 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"00bbf40\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"270\" height=\"213\" src=\"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/training-session-2.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-84\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3ec6b9e elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3ec6b9e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"740\" height=\"596\" src=\"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/ars-9-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-573\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/ars-9-1.jpg 740w, https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/ars-9-1-300x242.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bc195bb elementor-hidden-desktop elementor-hidden-tablet elementor-hidden-mobile e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"bc195bb\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-71446cc e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"71446cc\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bb1950e elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"bb1950e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"740\" height=\"596\" src=\"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/ars-